<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Posture Remedies - Gym_Era</title>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <h2 class="mb-4">ðŸ§˜ Fix Your Posture</h2>
        <p class="lead">Spend 5-10 minutes daily on these to counteract desk slouching and screen hunching.</p>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="/images/posture/neck-stretch.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Neck Stretch" style="height: 200px; object-fit: cover;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Neck Stretch</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Gently tilt head to each side, holding 30 sec. Relieves tech neck tension.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="/images/posture/chest-opener.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Chest Opener" style="height: 200px; object-fit: cover;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Chest Opener</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Clasp hands behind back, lift chest. Hold 30 sec. Counters rounded shoulders.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="/images/posture/cat-cow.png" class="card-img-top" alt="Cat Cow" style="height: 200px; object-fit: cover;">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">Cat-Cow Stretch</h5>
                        <p class="card-text">On all fours, alternate arching and rounding back. Improves spinal mobility.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
